{"type":"message","id":"cf910a6c","parentId":"6eb9ab9d","timestamp":"2026-02-27T02:50:37.898Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fyIfDhsMk5jlkBm2lzTvLYbj|fc_048a5081a4ffb0ee0169a1067b0b9c8199b79a414ea2b9b7a9","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.25 (4b5d4a4) — Ah, the fruit tree company! 🍎\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2602,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.25 (4b5d4a4) — Ah, the fruit tree company! 🍎\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron","cwd":"/home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772160637895}}
