sie` is already installed\n- `smart-route` is already installed\n- `daily-news-digest` is already installed\n\nPlease run this once on your machine (same workspace) after fixing gateway auth:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"Nashville Morning Brief (7:00 AM)\" \\\n  --description \"Daily Nashville morning brief using tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest\" \\\n  --cron \"0 7 * * *\" \\\n  --tz \"America/Chicago\" \\\n  --session isolated \\\n  --announce \\\n  --message 'Generate a concise Morning Brief tailored to Nashville, Tennessee, using ONLY these skills: tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest.\n\nOutput Structure (clean, brief, actionable):\n1) 🚗 Tesla Snapshot (Tessie)\n- Current battery % + estimated range\n- Charging status (charging / not charging) + current charge limit\n- Climate status + cabin temp (if available)\n- Any alerts (doors unlocked, windows open, sentry off, low tire pressure, etc.)\n- One clear recommendation if something needs attention\n\n2) 🛣️ Commute & Route (smart-route)\n- Focus: Nashville morning traffic (I-24, I-40, I-65)\n- Estimated drive time vs. typical for usual destination (e.g., Work)\n- Fastest current route + reason (traffic, incident, closure)\n- If delay > 10 min typical, suggested alternate route\n- If no saved destination, default contextual advice (e.g., check I-24 and I-65 traffic)\n\n3) 🗞️ Nashville News Digest (daily-news-digest)\n- Top 5 headlines max relevant to Nashville / Middle Tennessee\n- 1–2 sentence summary per headline\n- Highlight anything affecting the morning (weather alerts, road closures, major events)\n\nFormatting Rules:\n- Use bullet points; keep it skimmable\n- If a skill fails, mark that section Unavailable with a short reason\n- Keep total length ~250–350 words\n- Conclude with: **✅ Quick Focus:** <one actionable priority for your morning in Nashville>'\n```\n\nIf you want, I can also give you the exact 2-command fix for the gateway token mismatch.","textSignature":"msg_048a5081a4ff