 openclaw cron add --token \"$TOKEN\" --name \"Nashville Morning Brief (7:00 AM)\" --description \"Daily Nashville morning brief using tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest\" --cron \"0 7 * * *\" --tz \"America/Chicago\" --session isolated --announce --message \"Generate a concise Morning Brief tailored to Nashville, Tennessee, using ONLY these skills: tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest.\n\nOutput Structure (clean, brief, actionable):\n1) 🚗 Tesla Snapshot (Tessie)\n- Current battery % + estimated range\n- Charging status (charging / not charging) + current charge limit\n- Climate status + cabin temp (if available)\n- Any alerts (doors unlocked, windows open, sentry off, low tire pressure, etc.)\n- One clear recommendation if something needs attention\n\n2) 🛣️ Commute & Route (smart-route)\n- Focus: Nashville morning traffic (I-24, I-40, I-65)\n- Estimated drive time vs. typical for usual destination (e.g., Work)\n- Fastest current route + reason (traffic, incident, closure)\n- If delay > 10 min typical, suggested alternate route\n- If no saved destination, default contextual advice (e.g., check I-24 and I-65 traffic)\n\n3) 🗞️ Nashville News Digest (daily-news-digest)\n- Top 5 headlines max relevant to Nashville / Middle Tennessee\n- 1–2 sentence summary per headline\n- Highlight anything affecting the morning (weather alerts, road closures, major events)\n\nFormatting Rules:\n- Use bullet points; keep it skimmable\n- If a skill fails, mark that section Unavailable with a short reason\n- Keep total length ~250–350 words\n- Conclude with: **✅ Quick Focus:** <one actionable priority for your morning in Nashville>\" --json","timeout":120000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"TOKEN=$(systemctl --user show openclaw-gateway --property=Environment --value | tr ' ' '\\\\n' | sed -n 's/^OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN=//p'); openclaw cron add --token \\\"$TOKEN\\\" --name \\\"Nashville Morning Brief (7:00 AM)\\\" --description \\\"Daily Nashville morning brief using tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest\\\" --cron \\\"0 7 * * *\\\" --tz \\\"America/Chicago\\\" --session isolated --announce --message \\\"Generate a concise Morning Brief tailored to Nashville, Tennessee, using ONLY these skills: tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest.\\n\\nOutput Structure (clean, brief, actionable):\\n1) 🚗 Tesla Snapshot (Tessie)\\n- Current battery % + estimated range\\n- Charging status (charging / not charging) + current charge limit\\n- Climate status + cabin temp (if available)\\n- Any alerts (doors unlocked, windows open, sentry off, low tire pressure, etc.)\\n- One clear recommendation if something needs attention\\n\\n2) 🛣️ Commute & Route (smart-route)\\n- Focus: Nashville morning traffic (I-24, I-40, I-65)\\n- Estimated drive time vs. typical for usual destination (e.g., Work)\\n- Fastest current route + reason (traffic, incident, closure)\\n- If delay > 10 min typical, suggested alternate route\\n- If no saved destination, default contextual advice (e.g., check I-24 and I-65 traffic)\\n\\n3) 🗞️ Nashville News Digest (daily-news-digest)\\n- Top 5 headlines max relevant to Nashville / Middle Tennessee\\n- 1–2 sentence summary per headline\\n- Highlight anything affecting the morning (weather alerts, road closures, major events)\\n\\nFormatting Rules:\\n- Use bullet points; keep it skimmable\\n- If a skill fails, mark that section Unavailable with a short reason\\n- Keep total length ~250–350 words\\n- Conclude with: **✅ Quick Focus:** <one actionable priority for your morning in Nashville>\\\" --json\",\"timeout\":120000}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.3-codex","usage":{"input":436,"output":543,"cacheRead":30720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31699,"cost":{"input":0.000763,"output":0.007602,"cacheRead":0.005376,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013741}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772161424568}}
