{"type":"message","id":"bd816466","parentId":"094a7889","timestamp":"2026-02-27T03:06:54.331Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_HxIWf5MeKhaPHIaWu2UKU8Yf|fc_048a5081a4ffb0ee0169a10a4a6dc48199b61c3a8f5049d35e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"ac6cb972-3a5b-4f41-8bcd-ed5264ac20b0\",\n  \"name\": \"Nashville Morning Brief (7:00 AM)\",\n  \"description\": \"Daily Nashville morning brief using tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1772161436226,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1772161614244,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 7 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"America/Chicago\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Generate a concise Morning Brief tailored to Nashville, Tennessee, using ONLY these skills: tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest.\\n\\nOutput Structure (clean, brief, actionable):\\n1) 🚗 Tesla Snapshot (Tessie)\\n- Current battery % + estimated range\\n- Charging status (charging / not charging) + current charge limit\\n- Climate status + cabin temp (if available)\\n- Any alerts (doors unlocked, windows open, sentry off, low tire pressure, etc.)\\n- One clear recommendation if something needs attention\\n\\n2) 🛣️ Commute & Route (smart-route)\\n- Focus: Nashville morning traffic (I-24, I-40, I-65)\\n- Estimated drive time vs. typical for usual destination (e.g., Work)\\n- Fastest current route + reason (traffic, incident, closure)\\n- If delay > 10 min typical, suggested alternate route\\n- If no saved destination, default contextual advice (e.g., check I-24 and I-65 traffic)\\n\\n3) 🗞️ Nashville News Digest (daily-news-digest)\\n- Top 5 headlines max relevant to Nashville / Middle Tennessee\\n- 1–2 sentence summary per headline\\n- Highlight anything affecting the morning (weather alerts, road closures, major events)\\n\\nFormatting Rules:\\n- Use bullet points; keep it skimmable\\n- If a skill fails, mark that section Unavailable with a short reason\\n- Keep total length ~250–350 words\\n- Conclude with: **✅ Quick Focus:** <one actionable priority for your morning in Nashville>\",\n    \"model\": \"google/gemini-flash-latest\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"last\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772197200000,\n    \"lastError\": \"402 This request requires more credits, or fewer max_tokens. You requested up to 4096 tokens, but can only afford 206. To increase, visit https://openrouter.ai/settings/credits and upgrade to a paid account\",\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772161487908,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 5665,\n    \"lastDelivered\": true,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 1\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2874,"aggregated":"{\n  \"id\": \"ac6cb972-3a5b-4f41-8bcd-ed5264ac20b0\",\n  \"name\": \"Nashville Morning Brief (7:00 AM)\",\n  \"description\": \"Daily Nashville morning brief using tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1772161436226,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1772161614244,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 7 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"America/Chicago\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Generate a concise Morning Brief tailored to Nashville, Tennessee, using ONLY these skills: tessie, smart-route, daily-news-digest.\\n\\nOutput Structure (clean, brief, actionable):\\n1) 🚗 Tesla Snapshot (Tessie)\\n- Current battery % + estimated range\\n- Charging status (charging / not charging) + current charge limit\\n- Climate status + cabin temp (if available)\\n- Any alerts (doors unlocked, windows open, sentry off, low tire pressure, etc.)\\n- One clear recommendation if something needs attention\\n\\n2) 🛣️ Commute & Route (smart-route)\\n- Focus: Nashville morning traffic (I-24, I-40, I-65)\\n- Estimated drive time vs. typical for usual destination (e.g., Work)\\n- Fastest current route + reason (traffic, incident, closure)\\n- If delay > 10 min typical, suggested alternate route\\n- If no saved destination, default contextual advice (e.g., check I-24 and I-65 traffic)\\n\\n3) 🗞️ Nashville News Digest (daily-news-digest)\\n- Top 5 headlines max relevant to Nashville / Middle Tennessee\\n- 1–2 sentence summary per headline\\n- Highlight anything affecting the morning (weather alerts, road closures, major events)\\n\\nFormatting Rules:\\n- Use bullet points; keep it skimmable\\n- If a skill fails, mark that section Unavailable with a short reason\\n- Keep total length ~250–350 words\\n- Conclude with: **✅ Quick Focus:** <one actionable priority for your morning in Nashville>\",\n    \"model\": \"google/gemini-flash-latest\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"last\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772197200000,\n    \"lastError\": \"402 This request requires more credits, or fewer max_tokens. You requested up to 4096 tokens, but can only afford 206. To increase, visit https://openrouter.ai/settings/credits and upgrade to a paid account\",\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772161487908,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 5665,\n    \"lastDelivered\": true,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 1\n  }\n}","cwd":"/home/ec2-user/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772161614327}}
